1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 30=

3
00:00:18,239 --> 00:00:18,920
Chang...

4
00:00:19,440 --> 00:00:21,800
I...

5
00:00:24,440 --> 00:00:26,480
I didn't do it!

6
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:30,679
Take care of her.

7
00:00:36,799 --> 00:00:37,399
Wushuang!

8
00:00:39,320 --> 00:00:39,960
Wushuang!

9
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:41,200
Wushuang!

10
00:00:42,799 --> 00:00:43,479
Yu...

11
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:45,880
Get the first-aid kit!

12
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:47,520
Right here.

13
00:00:54,719 --> 00:00:55,359
Yu.

14
00:00:55,920 --> 00:00:56,840
You saw it yourself.

15
00:00:57,240 --> 00:00:59,920
Chu Yunchang is vicious.

16
00:01:01,399 --> 00:01:02,399
Go after her.

17
00:01:02,719 --> 00:01:04,159
You can't let her escape.

18
00:01:04,159 --> 00:01:04,760
But you...

19
00:01:05,959 --> 00:01:07,760
I'm fine. Just go!

20
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:09,959
Go now!

21
00:01:27,319 --> 00:01:27,959
Chang.

22
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,840
Did you kill that constable?

23
00:01:31,799 --> 00:01:32,519
I didn't.

24
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:34,079
She lunged right into it.

25
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,519
Yunchang is telling the truth.

26
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:36,680
That's what happened.

27
00:01:37,480 --> 00:01:38,719
That woman was willing to die

28
00:01:38,719 --> 00:01:39,959
just to frame you.

29
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:41,280
This isn't the time to talk.

30
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,319
Let's move.

31
00:01:42,319 --> 00:01:43,090
- All right.
- Let's go.

32
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:43,680
Yes.

33
00:01:48,799 --> 00:01:49,359
Move!

34
00:01:55,580 --> 00:01:56,920
Careful! The arrows are poisoned.

35
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,599
But I'm still here!

36
00:01:58,599 --> 00:02:00,519
The Gate Bureau
is trying to kill us all.

37
00:02:00,700 --> 00:02:02,239
How could you abandon your own cousin?

38
00:02:10,240 --> 00:02:10,759
Go!

39
00:02:14,312 --> 00:02:14,951
Hold on.

40
00:02:19,150 --> 00:02:20,260
Whose poison arrow is this?

41
00:02:21,062 --> 00:02:22,502
- Not mine.
- Not me.

42
00:02:25,719 --> 00:02:26,360
Oh no.

43
00:02:33,639 --> 00:02:34,199
My dear!

44
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:35,879
Madam.

45
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,537
It's the Gate Bureau's
Black-Clad Secret Guards.

46
00:02:37,537 --> 00:02:38,080
We need to go!

47
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:38,560
Quickly!

48
00:02:39,800 --> 00:02:40,599
Quickly!

49
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:43,960
It's a dead end.

50
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:46,599
Stop!

51
00:02:50,919 --> 00:02:51,560
Madam!

52
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:53,439
My dear!

53
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:16,919
You actually used poisoned bolts on me?

54
00:03:17,439 --> 00:03:18,199
I didn't do it.

55
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:20,639
Yu!

56
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:25,400
Wushuang.

57
00:03:25,400 --> 00:03:26,690
Were you going to leave me here?

58
00:03:27,719 --> 00:03:28,919
As a son of the Luo family,

59
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:31,080
we'll consider
you died in the line of duty.

60
00:03:43,520 --> 00:03:44,199
Yu.

61
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,400
Help us out!

62
00:03:45,879 --> 00:03:47,639
Don't forget you're a constable, too.

63
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:49,479
Master.

64
00:03:49,719 --> 00:03:51,120
Yunchang is the one you love.

65
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:55,360
Luo Wushuang!

66
00:03:55,639 --> 00:03:56,960
I've no grudge against you.

67
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,280
Why are you hounding us?

68
00:03:59,759 --> 00:04:01,520
I'm going to teach you a lesson!

69
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:39,550
♪Donning a mask to hide my heart♪

70
00:04:39,687 --> 00:04:43,412
♪Playing a part with a hollow smile♪

71
00:04:43,562 --> 00:04:47,125
♪Pitted against each other,
neither of us gives in♪

72
00:04:47,675 --> 00:04:51,750
♪One is cold as ice,
the other is burning like fire♪

73
00:04:51,775 --> 00:04:56,012
♪A love so deep,
yet destiny so fleeting♪

74
00:04:56,399 --> 00:04:57,040
Chang.

75
00:04:58,160 --> 00:04:59,319
That's enough.

76
00:05:00,062 --> 00:05:03,375
♪I long for it so much,
I crave to return♪

77
00:05:03,525 --> 00:05:07,137
♪To the moment we first met♪

78
00:05:07,150 --> 00:05:11,637
♪Casting aside all obsession
just to be with you♪

79
00:05:11,637 --> 00:05:15,649
♪Despite countless ordeals♪

80
00:05:15,725 --> 00:05:19,612
♪I can't untie the knot in your heart♪

81
00:05:19,712 --> 00:05:23,537
♪I end up creating another knot instead♪

82
00:05:23,762 --> 00:05:27,512
♪Unafraid of the distance,
I'm waiting for us to meet♪

83
00:05:27,637 --> 00:05:31,462
♪I'll spend my whole life by your side♪

84
00:05:32,262 --> 00:05:35,937
♪Even if tomorrow never comes♪

85
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:38,825
♪We move on to where it all began♪

86
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:39,590
Release the arrows!

87
00:05:39,712 --> 00:05:43,287
♪Worlds apart, I wait for our reunion♪

88
00:05:43,300 --> 00:05:47,575
♪But I'll spend my life
keeping you safe♪

89
00:05:48,839 --> 00:05:49,480
Chang!

90
00:05:51,412 --> 00:06:01,100
♪Let's return to when we first met♪

91
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,519
Yu!

92
00:06:06,399 --> 00:06:07,120
Yu!

93
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:15,600
They jumped.

94
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,360
Ms. Wushuang.

95
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,745
Chu Xiangling's been shot.

96
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:21,810
Mei Guangzu jumped into the river
with her and the  maid.

97
00:06:21,962 --> 00:06:22,762
Save Yu first.

98
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,439
Then, go after the Chu family.

99
00:06:24,439 --> 00:06:25,040
Understood.

100
00:06:29,839 --> 00:06:32,079
(How did things ever come to this?)

101
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,959
(Shen's Residence)
Quick! Get a healer, fast!

102
00:06:37,959 --> 00:06:38,519
Right away!

103
00:06:57,319 --> 00:06:58,900
Yunchang, it's me.

104
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:01,279
Shen Yidie.

105
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:07,839
Where am I?

106
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:09,800
You're at my family's house.

107
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,680
You were hurt, so I saved you.

108
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,720
What are you doing in Xichuan?

109
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:14,959
Who hurt you?

110
00:07:14,959 --> 00:07:15,839
Where's your family?

111
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:29,600
Thanks for saving me.

112
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,480
A bow from a beauty.

113
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,560
What a lucky girl I am.

114
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,600
You haven't recovered yet. Sit.

115
00:07:36,959 --> 00:07:38,399
If I were a man,

116
00:07:38,759 --> 00:07:39,720
I'd marry you.

117
00:07:41,439 --> 00:07:42,399
Stop teasing.

118
00:07:43,519 --> 00:07:46,040
I'd like to meet Lord Shen.

119
00:07:46,959 --> 00:07:47,920
My father?

120
00:07:49,879 --> 00:07:52,560
Lord Shen's ruled
the Xichuan underworld for years.

121
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,120
Now that I've come to Shu,

122
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:55,720
it's only right that I pay him a visit.

123
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:56,439
Besides,

124
00:07:57,519 --> 00:07:59,000
I have an important favor to ask.

125
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:02,000
Well...

126
00:08:02,439 --> 00:08:03,079
What is it?

127
00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:05,120
Is it a problem?

128
00:08:07,639 --> 00:08:09,240
Since you called off the wedding,

129
00:08:09,399 --> 00:08:12,639
my father's lost
a lot of face in the underworld.

130
00:08:13,519 --> 00:08:16,400
If you go to see him now,

131
00:08:16,512 --> 00:08:17,233
I'm afraid

132
00:08:18,360 --> 00:08:20,160
he won't be very welcoming.

133
00:08:33,279 --> 00:08:34,039
Over there!

134
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:36,919
Quick!

135
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:42,399
It's Constable Mao!

136
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:43,440
Tell Deputy Luo!

137
00:08:52,312 --> 00:08:54,100
Father, Sect Leader Chu
is here to see you.

138
00:08:54,450 --> 00:08:56,390
I, Yunchang, Sect Leader
of the Sacred Hand Sect,

139
00:08:57,025 --> 00:08:58,265
am here to pay my respects.

140
00:08:59,862 --> 00:09:02,382
(Shen Gongquan, Lord of Shen Manor)
It's an honor to have

141
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:03,840
Sect Leader Chu visit my manor.

142
00:09:06,559 --> 00:09:07,519
I'm truly ashamed

143
00:09:07,519 --> 00:09:08,480
that I'm at my wit's end.

144
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:10,279
If you weren't so desperate,

145
00:09:10,679 --> 00:09:12,000
I doubt you'd even give

146
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:14,480
my little manor a second look.

147
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,000
Father...

148
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:15,600
Quiet.

149
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,399
You're joking, Lord Shen.

150
00:09:19,840 --> 00:09:20,960
I came to Shu

151
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,840
specifically to pay you a visit.

152
00:09:23,519 --> 00:09:24,440
It's just that

153
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:26,960
we were ambushed
by the Gate Bureau on the way.

154
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:29,799
Now my aunt and uncle are missing.

155
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:32,480
I'd like to ask for your help
in finding them.

156
00:09:34,759 --> 00:09:36,300
You can leave that to me.

157
00:09:45,279 --> 00:09:47,679
I have one more favor to ask.

158
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,240
I'm listening.

159
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:54,480
Could you tell me where Dongfang Bai is?

160
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:59,039
You even know Dongfang Bai's with me?

161
00:10:00,300 --> 00:10:02,279
I really hope
you'll tell me the truth, Lord Shen.

162
00:10:04,639 --> 00:10:06,480
I can help you find Dongfang Bai.

163
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,279
I can help you get your revenge,

164
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:11,480
and I can even help you
rebuild the Sacred Hand Sect.

165
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:14,960
But how're you going to repay me?

166
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:20,720
What do you want from me?

167
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:25,879
Fulfill the marriage contract
with my son, Liefeng.

168
00:10:34,679 --> 00:10:36,000
(Shen Manor)
Give me a hand and take this over there.

169
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,590
- Yes.
- A bit to the left. Further left!

170
00:10:37,710 --> 00:10:38,960
- Is it straight now?
- It's done.

171
00:10:39,919 --> 00:10:40,720
Easy does it.

172
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,200
(Wedding)
Put the flowers over here.

173
00:10:42,559 --> 00:10:43,120
Got it.

174
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,100
Come over and help out.

175
00:10:45,712 --> 00:10:47,240
(Wedding)

176
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,240
Hurry up, you lot.

177
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:49,159
(Wedding. Bright Moon and Soft Breeze)

178
00:10:49,159 --> 00:10:50,080
Be careful with those!

179
00:10:50,080 --> 00:10:51,080
Make way, make way!

180
00:10:51,519 --> 00:10:52,360
Does this look good?

181
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:54,039
It's fine.

182
00:11:00,519 --> 00:11:01,159
Hey, buddy!

183
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,440
Get out here!

184
00:11:04,519 --> 00:11:05,279
Escort Zhao.

185
00:11:05,280 --> 00:11:06,190
Thanks for the hard work.

186
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:06,799
No problem.

187
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,600
Get your manager to settle the bill.

188
00:11:08,799 --> 00:11:09,919
Once I've unloaded this,

189
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:11,840
I've got to rush to Shen Manor
for the wedding!

190
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:14,039
Who's getting married?

191
00:11:15,919 --> 00:11:17,559
Shen Manor's eldest son
is taking a wife.

192
00:11:18,519 --> 00:11:19,720
Which family is the girl from?

193
00:11:20,080 --> 00:11:22,720
The Sect Leader of the Sacred Hand Sect.

194
00:11:23,112 --> 00:11:24,313
(Yunchang is at Shen Manor!)

195
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:26,480
(I've got to tell her aunt and uncle.)

196
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:29,850
(Shen Manor)

197
00:11:29,850 --> 00:11:30,771
Perfect timing.

198
00:11:30,960 --> 00:11:32,320
I've been searching for you.

199
00:11:33,087 --> 00:11:33,919
(Heartfelt Devotion, Wedding)

200
00:11:33,919 --> 00:11:34,770
Please, take a seat.

201
00:11:35,050 --> 00:11:35,519
Thank you.

202
00:11:35,519 --> 00:11:36,200
Sit, Madam.

203
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:36,840
My dear.

204
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:37,360
Father.

205
00:11:37,799 --> 00:11:39,480
Squire Mei and Mrs. Mei are here.

206
00:11:40,919 --> 00:11:42,519
You have graced this house

207
00:11:42,759 --> 00:11:44,940
with your visit today.

208
00:11:44,940 --> 00:11:46,700
Lord Shen, you are respected
throughout Xichuan.

209
00:11:46,700 --> 00:11:47,890
You're as formidable as ever.

210
00:11:47,919 --> 00:11:49,519
It's an honor for us to be here.

211
00:11:49,660 --> 00:11:50,482
Don't be so formal.

212
00:11:51,212 --> 00:11:53,375
I take it you're both here

213
00:11:53,375 --> 00:11:55,696
for your girl's wedding?

214
00:11:56,519 --> 00:11:57,159
Lord Shen.

215
00:11:57,840 --> 00:12:00,000
Is it true?
Is Chang really under your roof?

216
00:12:00,440 --> 00:12:01,080
Indeed.

217
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:03,759
She was being hunted by villains.

218
00:12:03,759 --> 00:12:05,279
It was my daughter who stepped in.

219
00:12:06,279 --> 00:12:07,840
But, what about the wedding?

220
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:10,080
Isn't that the arrangement

221
00:12:10,159 --> 00:12:11,720
our families made years ago?

222
00:12:11,919 --> 00:12:13,519
We're simply honoring that pact.

223
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:14,840
There's nothing odd about it.

224
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:16,399
But that engagement

225
00:12:16,519 --> 00:12:18,759
was called off back in the Capital.

226
00:12:19,159 --> 00:12:20,840
The Chu family may have backed out,

227
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:23,480
but our family never agreed to it.

228
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:24,360
Father!

229
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:25,840
I agreed to it.

230
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:26,679
Be quiet!

231
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:33,519
Yunchang!

232
00:12:35,759 --> 00:12:36,360
Auntie! Uncle!

233
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:37,279
Chang!

234
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,679
I've missed you both so much!

235
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:41,480
We've missed you too.

236
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,200
Let me look at you.

237
00:12:45,519 --> 00:12:46,559
How's the wound?

238
00:12:46,625 --> 00:12:47,506
It's just a scratch.

239
00:12:47,625 --> 00:12:49,385
You know I'm tougher than I look.

240
00:12:53,362 --> 00:12:54,522
Tell me, Chang,

241
00:12:54,787 --> 00:12:56,900
are you really marrying that cripple?

242
00:12:58,519 --> 00:13:00,639
Are they forcing your hand?

243
00:13:01,159 --> 00:13:02,159
If you aren't willing,

244
00:13:02,519 --> 00:13:03,679
just say the word.

245
00:13:04,159 --> 00:13:05,200
We'll fight our way out.

246
00:13:05,639 --> 00:13:06,679
The few of us

247
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,759
can surely handle that old man.

248
00:13:09,025 --> 00:13:09,785
Exactly.

249
00:13:10,279 --> 00:13:11,480
If I wanted to leave,

250
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:12,679
no one here could stop me.

251
00:13:13,279 --> 00:13:15,720
Even Shen Yidie offered
to let me slip away.

252
00:13:15,887 --> 00:13:16,926
Then, why haven't you left?

253
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:17,840
Yeah, why?

254
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,399
Because if I did,

255
00:13:19,896 --> 00:13:20,656
Shen Gongquan

256
00:13:20,656 --> 00:13:21,737
wouldn't ever tell us

257
00:13:21,737 --> 00:13:22,617
where Dongfang Bai is.

258
00:13:23,087 --> 00:13:24,886
But that's too great a price to pay.

259
00:13:24,900 --> 00:13:25,639
I won't allow it.

260
00:13:25,639 --> 00:13:26,279
Neither will I.

261
00:13:28,399 --> 00:13:29,519
This is nothing compared

262
00:13:29,879 --> 00:13:32,000
to what my father
and grandfather went through.

263
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:34,600
So...

264
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:37,840
What about Mao Buyu?

265
00:13:38,679 --> 00:13:40,960
Why are you bringing up
that heartbreaker again?

266
00:13:42,919 --> 00:13:43,519
Chang.

267
00:13:45,559 --> 00:13:46,559
Have you truly moved on?

268
00:13:48,799 --> 00:13:50,360
Of course I have.

269
00:14:03,500 --> 00:14:07,925
(Wedding)

270
00:14:07,925 --> 00:14:08,846
This way, please.

271
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:13,960
This way.

272
00:14:14,759 --> 00:14:15,720
Congratulations!

273
00:14:20,039 --> 00:14:21,879
Is there truly no other way?

274
00:14:22,712 --> 00:14:24,393
I can't bear to see Chang...

275
00:14:26,750 --> 00:14:28,469
marry that disabled son of theirs.

276
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:31,960
Calm yourself, my dear.

277
00:14:32,799 --> 00:14:34,559
Chang surely has a plan of her own.

278
00:14:42,399 --> 00:14:43,325
Esteemed heroes,

279
00:14:43,812 --> 00:14:45,213
my sincere thanks to you all

280
00:14:45,312 --> 00:14:47,832
for coming to celebrate
the union of my son, Liefeng,

281
00:14:47,919 --> 00:14:51,080
and the Sect Leader
of the Sacred Hand Sect, Chu Yunchang.

282
00:14:51,879 --> 00:14:54,440
Allow me to offer this toast
in your honor.

283
00:14:54,559 --> 00:14:55,360
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

284
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:55,679
Cheers!

285
00:14:55,679 --> 00:14:56,600
Bottoms up!

286
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:57,639
Congratulations, Lord Shen!

287
00:14:57,639 --> 00:14:58,480
- Cheers!
- Cheer!

288
00:14:58,480 --> 00:14:59,360
Congratulations.

289
00:14:59,559 --> 00:15:00,120
Cheers.

290
00:15:03,919 --> 00:15:06,080
The bride and groom have arrived!

291
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:07,679
- Wonderful!
- Great!

292
00:15:08,399 --> 00:15:09,120
Wonderful!

293
00:15:18,575 --> 00:15:22,960
(Shen Manor)

294
00:15:22,960 --> 00:15:23,600
Deputy.

295
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,320
This is the place.

296
00:15:25,437 --> 00:15:26,957
Yu, you are still hurt.

297
00:15:27,312 --> 00:15:28,473
You need not fight.

298
00:15:29,587 --> 00:15:31,950
Black-Clad Secret Guards,
follow me and seize the outlaws.

299
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:33,120
Deputy Luo.

300
00:15:33,720 --> 00:15:35,320
If you just barge in there,

301
00:15:35,480 --> 00:15:36,639
it'll be inappropriate.

302
00:15:36,639 --> 00:15:37,759
I'm here to arrest criminals.

303
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:39,240
To whom do I have to answer?

304
00:15:39,879 --> 00:15:41,360
You don't know the rules here.

305
00:15:41,875 --> 00:15:43,316
If you force your way in,

306
00:15:43,639 --> 00:15:45,919
I'm afraid there will be trouble.

307
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:47,559
No matter the rules here,

308
00:15:48,120 --> 00:15:49,799
they do not override
the law of the land.

309
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:52,240
(Wedding, Bright Moon and Soft Breeze)
First bow to Heaven and Earth!

310
00:15:52,240 --> 00:15:53,840
Wonderful!

311
00:15:54,519 --> 00:15:56,480
Second bow to the parents!

312
00:15:56,912 --> 00:15:58,471
- Splendid!
- Wonderful!

313
00:15:59,159 --> 00:16:00,000
Correct.

314
00:16:02,639 --> 00:16:03,200
Great.

315
00:16:04,679 --> 00:16:06,639
Congratulations!

316
00:16:07,639 --> 00:16:08,159
Yu!

317
00:16:08,159 --> 00:16:09,440
Congratulations, Lord Shen.

318
00:16:10,200 --> 00:16:12,360
Bow to each other!

319
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:14,320
Surround them!

320
00:16:18,275 --> 00:16:22,237
♪Donning a mask to hide my heart♪

321
00:16:22,350 --> 00:16:25,800
♪Playing a part with a hollow smile♪

322
00:16:26,425 --> 00:16:30,150
♪Pitted against each other,
neither of us gives in♪

323
00:16:30,375 --> 00:16:34,000
♪One is cold as ice,
the other is burning like fire♪

324
00:16:34,362 --> 00:16:38,225
♪A love so deep,
yet destiny so fleeting♪

325
00:16:38,350 --> 00:16:41,750
♪This fervor is buried deep within♪

326
00:16:47,175 --> 00:16:50,450
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

327
00:16:50,488 --> 00:16:53,363
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

328
00:16:53,863 --> 00:16:59,581
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

329
00:17:00,763 --> 00:17:04,083
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

330
00:17:04,213 --> 00:17:07,133
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

331
00:17:08,301 --> 00:17:13,541
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

332
00:17:14,763 --> 00:17:17,156
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

333
00:17:17,156 --> 00:17:20,806
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

334
00:17:20,875 --> 00:17:24,365
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

335
00:17:24,463 --> 00:17:27,438
♪To the ends of time♪

336
00:17:27,438 --> 00:17:30,813
♪The moon traces your face♪

337
00:17:31,000 --> 00:17:34,588
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

338
00:17:34,588 --> 00:17:40,828
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

339
00:17:41,163 --> 00:17:44,378
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

340
00:17:44,663 --> 00:17:48,201
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

341
00:17:48,488 --> 00:17:51,513
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

342
00:17:51,513 --> 00:17:54,613
♪On our way to forever♪

343
00:17:54,613 --> 00:17:58,463
♪The moon traces your face♪

344
00:17:58,463 --> 00:18:01,823
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

345
00:18:02,013 --> 00:18:07,973
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

346
00:18:09,050 --> 00:18:18,690
♪Just to be with you♪
